title: Bobby Makes Announcement + Shock Collar Spelling Bee + Amy Takes Her Kids To Meet Their Neighbors
itunes:title: Bobby Makes Announcement + Shock Collar Spelling Bee + Amy Takes Her Kids To Meet Their Neighbors
description:
The show, including Bobby, participates in a Shock Collar Spelling Bee. Each misspelled word means a shock! Amy talks about taking her kids to meet their neighbors and drop off cookies. Lunchbox tries to go viral singing reggae music in grocery store.
